snippet.title: Rue - Alpha  Build Gameplay ~ Dark Dimension
snippet.description:
This is footage of the alpha build made for the game "Rue". It is a card game about people trying to grab the rose from each other. It is available for Windows, Linux and Android.

The game is not complete yet, but it is free and open-source, in the hopes that users will enjoy it until it is done.

Check it out here: https://darkdimension.org/games/rue.html

~~~

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/darkdimensiongd
Support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/darkdimension
